title: 09 October 2015 - Lisburn director disqualified (Department of Enterprise, Trade and Investment)
text: ( Source : Department of Enterprise , Trade and Investment) A Lisburn director has been disqualified in respect of her conduct as a director of a restaurant business. ~ Friday, 9 October 2015 Perpetua Teresa Hughes (42) of Barleywood Mill ,
